<h1 class='text-center'><span class="border border-3">Medical Information Notepad</span></h1>
<h1 class='text-center'><span class="border border-3">List of Identifiers For <%= @patient.username %>:</span></h1><br><br>
<h2 class='text-center'><span class="border border-3">Choose The Identifier For The Note, Items, Or Questions</span></h2>
